Project 01

This program will display a 3D model with a realistic shadow. A discussion of potential problems and issues with my implementation is included in REPORT.

Usage:
	Run "make" in this directory to compile the program.
	Run "./main ModelFile.t" to execute the program and specify a .t file to read in.

List of files:
	main.cpp		// Entry point of the application, everything is in here
	mat4x4.h		// File provided for project, performs matrix multiplication for the trackball
	vec3d.h			// File provided for project, performs vector operations
	Makefile		// Configuration file to compile the project
	REPORT			// Write up of potential issues with the algorithm
	README			// This file